  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large paella pan or skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook for 3-4 minutes or until translucent.",
    "Add the diced bell pepper and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they release their liquid and start to brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the artichoke hearts, diced tomato, smoked paprika, and garlic powder. Cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Pour in the saffron-infused vegetable broth and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-12 minutes or until the liquid has been absorbed and the rice is tender.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot."
  ],
